MarkitupRails
=============

Markitup[1] plugin for Ruby on Rails.


Example
=======

<head>
 <%= include_markitup_assets %>
 <%= include_markitup_assets :sets => :markdown, :skin => :simple
</head>
<body>

    <textarea id="markitup" ...>
    <%= init_markitup_for("#markitup") %>

</body>


[1] http://markitup.jaysalvat.com/home/

